name: POWERSKULL_02 - Transmutational Healing Cranium
description:
Master Alchemists of an ancient tribe from the extinct planet 396-Gamma were responsible for crafting all the POWERSKULLZ.

The Legends from the Great Elders describe how this Transmutational Healing Cranium instantly healed whoever grabbed it with both hands and raised it to eye level.

This healing artefact would work only when held by a human being. The skull's resonant frequency is in tune with the electromagnetic field emanated by humans. The unique electromagnetic field signature of the human carrying the Transmutational Healing Cranium would be tuned back to its healthy pattern, thus transmuting disease at the quantum level.

Other living forms' magnetic fields would not be tuned to the Transmutational Healing Cranium and would not activate it.

The POWERSKULLZ are part of the POWERVERSE, a reality where humans have achieved their highest potential and live as gods.
